      • findHorseSpace

        public int findHorseSpace​(java.lang.String name)
        Returns the index of the space that contains the horse with the specified name. Precondition: No two horses in the barn have the same name.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the horse to find
        Returns:
        the index of the space containing the horse with the specified name; -1 if no horse with the specified name is in the barn.

      • consolidate

        public void consolidate()
        Consolidates the barn by moving horses so that the horses are in adjacent spaces, starting at index 0, with no empty space between any two horses. Postcondition: The order of the horses is the same as before the consolidation.
